Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼大人她…
